# Help Center

Get help about a topic by typing `/help <topic>` in the chat. Here are some topics you can get help with:

-  `command`: Get help on how to use commands.
    -   `/help explain`
    -   `/help contact`
-  `concept`: Get help on a concept.
    -   `/help energy`
    -   `/help buy energy`
    -   `/help earn energy`
    -   `/help sell energy`
    -   `/help send message`

If you still have questions, you can ask them in the chat using the _*@support*_ handle and our support agent will do its best to help you.
